Fatima Togbe, onye aha ya zuru oke bụ Kike Fatima Togbe-Olory, bụ onye guzobere na onye isi nchịkwa nke Hayati Communications Group, ụlọ ọrụ mgbasa ozi na ntụrụndụ nke na-elekwasị anya n'ịkwalite ndụ ụmụ nwanyị Alakụba ike na West Africa. Ọ malitere Hayati Magazine n'afọ 2012, Hayati Retail n'afọ 2015, Hayati Fashion Week na July 2017, na Hayati Magazine Français na October 2017.
Fatima pụtara na abụọ maka mgbasa ozi Vlisco nke afọ 2017 (S2-2017 na S3-2017), nke na-eme ememe ụzọ dị iche iche na nke pụrụ iche ụmụ nwanyị Afrịka na-eyi vlisco
Ọ nọchitere anya ụdị Nestle, Goldern Morn Naịjịrịa na Maggi, dị ka onye nnọchi anya ha.
